response.overview: Hi! I'm Diane Spencer, a British female comedian. This is my eighth full comedy special where I do jokes about paranoia, attempting to buy drugs, offending new relatives and online gaming.  As a stand-up comedian, I'm constantly working in comedy clubs and I post a full standup show about once every fifteen months! I'll post short jokes from that show and the occasional vlog so please subscribe so you don't miss anything. Please do comment I enjoy reading them.  All material written and performed by Diane Spencer. Voiceover/Interviewer: Kevin Shepherd Ingame footage from Rust, Facepunch Studios. Filmed at The Museum of Comedy, St Georges Church, London on Nov 15, 2018. Filmed by Little Lens Video - littlelensvideo.com All material copyright Diane Spencer 2018.
response.title: Noob: Live Standup Special
